# MQTT Protocol Utilities Module (Facade)
# Supports MQTT v3.1.1 and v5.0
# Pure Simple implementation with no runtime limitations

# Module Organization:
# - types.spl: Constants and packet structures
# - packet.spl: Encoding/decoding utilities and fixed headers
# - connect.spl: CONNECT/CONNACK/DISCONNECT/AUTH packets
# - publish.spl: PUBLISH/PUBACK/PUBREC/PUBREL/PUBCOMP packets
# - subscribe.spl: SUBSCRIBE/SUBACK/UNSUBSCRIBE/UNSUBACK packets
# - utilities.spl: Topic matching, validation, properties, helpers

# All public functions are accessible from this facade module
